{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"RTL（从右到左）","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/rtl","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>RTL</strong>（<strong>从右到左</strong>，Right To Left）是<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Locale\">区域设置 <small>(en-US)</small></a>的属性之一，用于指示语言从右到左的书写方向。</p>\n<p>举个例子，希伯来语（<code>he</code>）指定从右往左书写，而阿拉伯语（<code>ar</code>）也是另一种从右往左书写的常见语言。</p>\n<p>与 RTL 相对的是 LTR（从左到右，Left To Right），用于包括英语（<code>en</code>、<code>en-US</code>、<code>en-GB</code> 等等）、西班牙语（<code>es</code>）及法语（<code>fr</code>）在内的其他语言。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary\">MDN Web 文档术语</a>\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Localization\">本地化</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/ltr\">LTR（从左到右）</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/rtl\" aria-current=\"page\">RTL（从右到左）</a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"RTL（从右到左，Right To Left）是区域设置 (en-US)的属性之一，用于指示语言从右到左的书写方向。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"RTL (Right to Left)","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"rtl","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"RTL (右書き)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/rtl","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/rtl/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/rtl","title":"RTL（从右到左）"}],"pageTitle":"RTL（从右到左） - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}